## encryption
**[optional] object**

[ğŸ“– Documentation](<https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/azurerm/latest/docs/resources/automation_account#encryption>) | [ğŸ” See Related Issues](<https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-provider-azurerm/issues?q=is:issue azurerm_automation_account encryption>) | [ğŸ› Raise Issue](<https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-provider-azurerm/issues/new?template=Bug_Report.yml&title=`azurerm_automation_account` - encryption >)

An `encryption` block as defined below.

 - key_vault_key_id: The ID of the Key Vault Key which should be used to Encrypt the data in this Automation Account.
 - key_source: UnDocumented
 - user_assigned_identity_id: The User Assigned Managed Identity ID to be used for accessing the Customer Managed Key for encryption.

An `identity` block as defined below.

 - type: The type of identity used for this Automation Account. Possible values are `SystemAssigned`, `UserAssigned` and `SystemAssigned, UserAssigned`.
 - identity_ids: The ID of the User Assigned Identity which should be assigned to this Automation Account.
